1. *Novih* radnika je stiglo u firmu. (New workers have arrived at the company.)
2. Nema *novih* informacija o događaju. (There are no new information about the event.)
3. Potrebna je veća količina *novih* materijala. (A greater amount of new materials is needed.)
4. Učenici su učili o *novih* pojmovima. (The students were learning about new concepts.)
5. Ona je otkrila *novih* mogućnosti. (She discovered new possibilities.)